video.title: How "It's Always Sunny in Philadelphia" Changed Comedy Forever
video.description: "It's Always Sunny in Philadelphia" is one of the best, if not the definitive best comedy shows ever made. In this video, I break down what makes Sunny so great and how it has changed the way we view comedy forever.
